order widget makes this not practical.", "It sucks üëé I don't know how to use it.. It wont open. I restarted my phone just to see if it would work and nothing happened", 'Awesome. Thank you so much for developing this simple and brilliant app, the features of which are inexplicably not baked into the Android Spotify App in the first place. Yes, it could be more refined, but it is simple and it works. Bear in mind you can create as many widgets as you like and they will all still work. Brilliant app. 5 stars.', "Used to be so awesome but now appears to be broken!! Please please fix it, \nI rely on this every day and it's criminal that Spotify itself doesn't \noffer a similar widget", 'Would be great if we could edit the opacity of the widget in order to make it transparent, that would be perfect for most of us.', 'Great app but would give 5 if I could have transparent background', 'Great app. Does exactly what it claims. I had to restart phone on install, but everything worked great after that', 'Game changer! Thank you so much! Would be nice to be able to change playlists after the widget is added though...', "Please add transparent widgets as well and I'll give you 5 stars! ‚ù§Ô∏è", "It doesn't work for me", "It sucks doesn't even let me put it on home screen", 'Quick and easy way to play any of my playlists.', "Needs adjustable transparency other than that it's great", 'Transparent background and autoplay would make it perfect. Still does everything I need.', 'This sucks never use it', 'Says what it does üòù'], 'appId': 'com.wavy.spotifyplaylistwidget', 'url': 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wavy.spotifyplaylistwidget&hl=en&gl=us'}
